description: "This should interest you: we have a small team researching new, stronger health stims, but we're low on certain materials that were never restocked on station. Head to the Vaccine Labs and bring back some Medical Supplies."
chainDescription:
Osiris specialize in medical tech, from surgical robots to powerful medicines and even healing nanites. Many of their advancements are only possible thanks to prospectors like you retrieving samples from the planet.

Get Osiris what they need, and you'll be rewarded with access to new, stronger health stims.

description: "There are a few more items from the surface our team needs, Prospector. Get what we need from this list if you want access to stronger stims."
